{"lastModified":1773084691143,"uri":"c::20370734480::vessel::89fd0680-9df3-11f0-947c-5f3d4f9d4569","yachtType":["Sailing","Gulet"],"description":"Operating Area: Greek Islands – Dodecanese, Saronic Islands, Ionian Sea, Mediterranean\n\nThe ZELDA yacht is an elegant and luxurious 40.40-meter sailing yacht that offers an unparalleled charter experience in the scenic waters of Greece. Built by the renowned yacht builder SU Marine in 2010, ZELDA combines classic charm with modern amenities to deliver an exceptional yachting adventure.\n\nWith a thoughtful layout that includes five spacious cabins, ZELDA accommodates up to 10 guests in total comfort. Each cabin is located on the lower deck, providing privacy and tranquility for all on board. The master cabin features a king-size bed and an ensuite bathroom, providing a retreat-like feel with ample space. The yacht also boasts two VIP cabins, each with a queen-size bed, as well as two additional guest cabins with double beds, all equipped with ensuite facilities for added convenience.\n\nDesigned to be both comfortable and elegant, ZELDA offers indoor and outdoor spaces ideal for relaxation, socializing, and enjoying the panoramic views of Greece’s iconic coastlines.","blueprint":{"name":"ZELDA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::89fd0680-9df3-11f0-947c-5f3d4f9d4569::assets::71ed9050-9df8-11f0-92f9-f78c3cb8e879/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::89fd0680-9df3-11f0-947c-5f3d4f9d4569::assets::8043df20-9df7-11f0-92f9-f78c3cb8e879/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::89fd0680-9df3-11f0-947c-5f3d4f9d4569::assets::641ab440-9df7-11f0-92f9-f78c3cb8e879/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::89fd0680-9df3-11f0-947c-5f3d4f9d4569::assets::6418b870-9df7-11f0-92f9-f78c3cb8e879/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::89fd0680-9df3-11f0-947c-5f3d4f9d4569::assets::52e1d460-9df7-11f0-92f9-f78c3cb8e879/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::89fd0680-9df3-11f0-947c-5f3d4f9d4569: